---
layout: base.njk
active: awards
title: Awards
---
{#
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  This list is driven by content/awards/list.json (the global `awards`), an
  ordered array. JSON can't hold comments, so the reference shape lives here
  (it never renders). Reorder awards by moving entries in the array.

  Two entry shapes:
    Simple (default) — one line, no detail page, no extra files:
        { "title": "Award Name", "description": "One-line summary." }
      `description` is optional and supports inline Markdown links.

    Detailed — references a Markdown file in content/awards/ that holds the
    title, description, and a body, and gets its own detail page:
        { "ref": "vex-skills-world-champions" }   // -> content/awards/vex-skills-world-champions.md
      The .md uses the same front matter as experiences/projects (title, date,
      description, optional website/location) plus a Markdown body. Its title
      links to /awards/<slug>/. The array only positions it in the list.

  Reference shapes:

      [
        { "title": "Hackathon Winner", "description": "First place." },
        { "ref": "vex-skills-world-champions" }
      ]
  ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#}
<h1 class="page-title">Awards</h1>
<ul class="entry-list">
  {% for a in awards %}
  {%- if a.ref -%}
  {# Detailed award: pull title/description from its .md collection item. #}
  {%- set item = collections.awards | findBySlug(a.ref) -%}
  {%- if item -%}
  <li class="entry-row">
    <div class="entry-head">
      <a class="entry-title" href="{{ item.url | url }}">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
    </div>
    {% if item.data.description %}<p class="entry-desc">{{ item.data.description | mdInline | safe }}</p>{% endif %}
  </li>
  {%- endif -%}
  {%- else -%}
  {# Simple award: title (optionally an external link) + description. #}
  <li class="entry-row">
    <div class="entry-head">
      {% if a.website %}<a class="entry-title entry-title--ext" href="{{ a.website }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ a.title }}</a>{% else %}<span class="entry-title">{{ a.title }}</span>{% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if a.description %}<p class="entry-desc">{{ a.description | mdInline | safe }}</p>{% endif %}
  </li>
  {%- endif -%}
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
